        body: '<pre>@import "other_file_path"</pre><div>Allows you to include the content of one file in another. You don\'t need to add the extension, just the name of the file.<br>Any variables or mixins declared in the imported file can be used now in your file<br>question: what about functions???<br><br></div>',
