        name: 'example',
        body: '<div>If you prefix the name of a file with an underscore:</div><pre>_my_file.scss</pre><div><br>the file won\'t be transpiled until we do:</div><pre>@import "my_file"</pre><div><br>*Note we don\'t include the prefix underscore when importing</div>',
