        body: '<div>Just as you would imagine. Very useful to create a <em>rythm</em>.<br><br></div><pre><strong>@function</strong> <strong>pow</strong>($base<strong>,</strong> $exponent) {\r\n  $result: 1;\r\n  <strong>@for</strong> $_ <strong>from</strong> 1 <strong>through</strong> $exponent {\r\n    $result: $result <strong>*</strong> $base;\r\n  }\r\n  <strong>@return</strong> $result;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<strong>.sidebar</strong> {\r\n  <strong>float</strong>: left;\r\n  <strong>margin-left</strong>: <strong>pow</strong>(4<strong>,</strong> 3) <strong>*</strong> 1px;\r\n}</pre><div><br></div>',
