        body: '<pre>@startuml\r\n\r\nobject user\r\n\r\nuser : name = "Dummy"\r\nuser : id = 123\r\n\r\n@enduml</pre><div><br>or another -and easier- way of doing it:<br><br></div><pre>@startuml\r\n\r\nobject user {\r\n  name = "Dummy"\r\n  id = 123\r\n}\r\n\r\n@enduml</pre><div><br><action-text-attachment content-type="image" url="https://www.planttext.com/api/plantuml/img/SoWkIImgAStDuUBAJyfAJIvHA2rEBUBY0f4ALWfvYRcf2hOAIYwbkRcLIZ3Hp1IWcA6HCHUNGsfU2b0p0000" width="131" height="69"></action-text-attachment></div>',
