        name: 'example',
        body: '<div>sudo chown patty myfile  ==&gt; will set the ownership of myfile to patty<br><br>sudo chgrp whales myfile ==&gt; will set the group of myfile to whales<br><br>And doing the two at once:<br><br>sudo chown patty:whales myfile</div>',
