        id: 294,
        name: 'example',
        body: '<div>This is what you are mostly going to use to deal with events. You have to install it<br><br></div><pre>npm install --save-dev @testing-library/user-event</pre><div><br>Basically all the events that you can do. check docs in <a href="https://testing-library.com/docs/ecosystem-user-event">here</a>.</div><div><br></div>',
